{"tid":563454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港「野豬王」翻垃圾桶覓食 威脅鄰近小學","createTime":"2018-02-17T03:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T05:02:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2fc365bc3b0233c1260493d7fa3daa1699ebb1","tid":563454,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/02/pig-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fpig-600x400.jpg&h=d6fd602e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更新: 2018-02-14 1:12 PM\t   標籤: 香港, 野豬, 小學, 絕育, 覓食<br />\n【大紀元2018年02月14日訊】（大紀元記者陳俊村報導）網上熱傳的一段視頻顯示，香港有隻體型巨大的野豬趴在垃圾桶上覓食，而其附近就有一所小學，這讓家長們擔心孩子們的安全問題。<br />\n<br />\n這段視頻由臉書用戶涂東東分享，自2月6日上傳至今，觀看人次已超過60萬，轉分享次數超過7000次。<br />\n<br />\n該視頻顯示，這隻「野豬王」以兩條後腿站立、兩條前腿趴在垃圾桶上的方式，在垃圾堆裡翻找食物。牠的體型壯碩，幾乎是其它野豬的幾倍大。而其它野豬似乎也先「禮讓」牠就食。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》報導說，有一所小學近在咫尺，當家長們送孩子去上學時，他們都看到這隻令人害怕的「野豬王」，而且擔心牠的尖牙和蠻力會對人構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n儘管有網民對這些野豬表達擔憂之意，但也有人表示，這是司空見慣的事情，因為牠們沒有足夠的食物可以吃。<br />\n<br />\n另有網民說，很多野豬很餓，以至於到農田裡偷吃農作物。<br />\n<br />\n而香港媒體報導說，野豬在香港市區出沒，或在馬路上散步，也非新鮮事。去年12月，甚至有8隻野豬闖入海洋公園遊客區覓食。而在漁護署人員接報趕到現場前，這些野豬已返回附近山上。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署稱，野豬在香港分布範圍廣泛，而且十分常見。牠們通常在山林棲息，偶爾會受棄置食物吸引，走近民居覓食。<br />\n<br />\n由於野豬在香港幾乎沒有天敵，加上繁殖力強，所以野豬數目急增。該署正在研擬為野豬注射避孕藥物的方法，來控制牠們的數量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/2/14/n10142446.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F18%2F2%2F14%2Fn10142446.htm&d=JIlxGgzyIxv6YoIyY9fM5v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8a6a9296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/2/14/n10142446.htm</a>"},{"pid":"25ce181d6bdf5d2b6fd69b4d606ab38a1441baa7","tid":563454,"uid":941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://goo.gl/images/8JtrdG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fimages%2F8JtrdG&h=41ecc6f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08185206220c3b5a4ce2dcbffb395d6630bd166e","tid":563454,"uid":941,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/112011_427949deab5f1c72a731e6ba83ec4304.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F112011_427949deab5f1c72a731e6ba83ec4304.png&h=d7c9020d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02e0a1d413257c52e4187092ebcbe17cbce28495","tid":563454,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係又想捉丫嘛"},{"pid":"2c93d9d0e887cd6d6cee711cf15402883962f807","tid":563454,"uid":33878,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:27:41.000Z","msg":"人仲可怕"},{"pid":"b627519666245d1f51f64f5c8cdf5d7598e62b50","tid":563454,"uid":32976,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:37:30.000Z","msg":"邊個威脅邊個啊！"},{"pid":"9d18a341d570122ef6c76655b9ecdddb6789e93b","tid":563454,"uid":139815,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:41:03.000Z","msg":"我們連登仔只要出手,單手就能殺死野豬王"},{"pid":"88ee1ab82432af8575090dcfec71994dff702c7c","tid":563454,"uid":48276,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:46:46.000Z","msg":"野豬肉質同味道唔知點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0c99927c9d0e7a8fa8c19a4618a410c1363225","tid":563454,"uid":50801,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"住既地方俾新移民侵佔，生活空間縮細，搵食空間縮細，仲要俾新移民惡人先告狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711de73ab116daf4b88d9b439183184391fa4f35","tid":563454,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu